name: DATA NEVER DIES: YOU ONLY LIVE ONCE BUT YOUR DATA IS FOREVER (KR/EN)
description: From the "Think Privacy" series of motivational privacy posters first launched in 2016 at the New Museum Store in NYC as part of the Privacy Gift Shop. This bilingual design was created for the Seoul Mediacity Biennale 2018 Future Shop. Edition of 20. Format: A2, 7016 x 4961 pixels, PNG, Korean/English. Created in 2018.
